                <div class="module__content">Set the foundation. How photogrammetry works, what separates survey-grade from consumer-grade output, and what a complete court-defensible deliverable actually looks like. GSD, point clouds, orthomosaics, overlap percentages — explained from an investigator's perspective. You'll also get set up with your included software before the first field session.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="module">
              <div class="module__header">
                <div class="module__number">02</div>
