                <div class="module__content">The module that separates this course from every basic UAS program. GCP deployment strategy, RTK rover operation, and the decision framework for choosing between RTK, PPK, and traditional GCP based on your scene and equipment. Includes a live field exercise deploying GCPs at the training site.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

