              </div>
              <div class="module__body">
                <div class="module__content">Grid and oblique patterns, overlap settings, GSD targets — executed under real scene constraints. We include dedicated instruction on after-dark missions: lighting strategies, camera settings, and the adjustments needed to capture usable data when the scene doesn't cooperate with daylight. Students execute a live mapping flight.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="module">
              <div class="module__header">
                <div class="module__number">04</div>
                <div class="module__title">Photogrammetric Processing Workflow</div>
