              <div class="module__body">
                <div class="module__content">Image alignment, dense cloud generation, mesh creation, and orthomosaic production — run step by step using your included software on data you captured in the field. We cover the common processing failures and how to diagnose and fix them before they become courtroom problems.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="module">
              <div class="module__header">
                <div class="module__number">05</div>
                <div class="module__title">Accuracy Validation &amp; Court-Ready Documentation</div>
