              </div>
              <div class="module__body">
                <div class="module__content">Checkpoint verification, RMSE calculation, and GSD confirmation — documented in a format sufficient to defend your findings in court. You'll know exactly what to record, how to record it, and how to present your accuracy numbers when the defense challenges your methodology.</div>
              </div>
            </div>

